author: Giorgio Mendoza
description: AAEON has launched two new developer boards under its UP brand: the UP TWL and UP TWLS. Based on Intel’s N-series platform (formerly Twin Lake), the UP TWL targets classic development needs, while the UP TWLS offers a slimmer layout for compact, IoT-oriented use. Both boards can be configured with the Intel Core i3-N355, Intel […]
title: AAEON Adds to UP Lineup with UP TWL and UP TWLS Developer Boards for Edge and IoT Applications
